        "text": "Israel took all these cities and dwelt in all the cities of the Amorites, Ḥeshbon and her towns",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Anciently this part of the Plateau was thickly populated. From almost every elevation several groups of ruins are visible, mostly Byzantine, but how much older each site may be cannot yet be said. The land is very good for corn.",
